8-0.query:
SELECT *
FROM aka_name AS an,
 cast_info AS ci,
 company_name AS cn,
 movie_companies AS mc,
 name AS n,
 role_type AS rt,
 title AS t
WHERE an.person_id = n.id
 AND n.id = ci.person_id
 AND ci.movie_id = t.id
 AND t.id = mc.movie_id
 AND mc.company_id = cn.id
 AND ci.role_id = rt.id
 AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
 AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
AND ci.note = '@param0'
AND cn.country_code = '@param1'
AND mc.note LIKE '@param2'
AND mc.note NOT LIKE '@param3'
AND n.name LIKE '@param4'
AND n.name NOT LIKE '@param5'
AND rt.role = '@param6';
